COMPONENT NAME: LKM Object Storage to ADWC Copy COMPONENT VERSION: 1 AUTHOR: Oracle COMPATIBILITY: ODI 12.2.1.4.0 or above
DESCRIPTION This LKM will load data from Oracle Cloud Object Storage to Oracle Autonomous Data Warehouse Cloud. It is using dbms_cloud.copy_data() function to load data into a staging table. It has to be used in combination with Oracle or generic SQL IKM.
